        "type": "stat_block_section",
        "subtype": "feat",
        "text": "The devastation wrought by your large-scale spells is particularly terrifying. If the next action you use is to Cast a Spell that deals damage in an area, any target who fails their saving throw is also frightened 1 (or frightened 2 on a critical failure).",
